Arcangel/Fury



Arcangel looked at Hot Rod he did not want to kill him but he wanted to cook 
meat over Felines roasting body. Then he had a idea.



Arcangel open his chest plate and pulled out the maximal matrix.



Arcangel:




"you all know what this lets see what would happen if I used this. If I can. 
Hot Rod time to put your spark back into place."



As he opened weird fellings started to go over him. He could not tell what 
was happening life,truth,Justice,love,peace,darkness,evil, and pain all came 
to his mined at once. He was changing again this time. he could feel more 
power then ever he was Angel Prime. Then a huge blue blast came at Hot Rod 
to change him back to a maximal. Arcangel was bigger and older looking his 
blue and silver armor shined better then ever. his eyes burned like fire. He 
was truely the next Prime to rise.



Fury fired a net at Feline then transformed and fell backwards at the sight 
of Angel Prime.
